    77→/// <summary>
    78→/// High-performance, lock-free in-memory event bus optimized for a modular
    79→/// monolith. The implementation uses <see cref="System.Threading.Channels"/>
    80→/// to guarantee FIFO ordering, back-pressure and bounded concurrency.
