    14→    ///     Internally delegates to strategy implementations that understand the
    15→    ///     concrete token standard (e.g. ERC-20-like, ERC-721-like).
    16→    ///     
    17→    ///     TokenService is designed to be thread-safe, idempotent where possible,
    18→    ///     and fully asynchronous.  
    19→    ///     
    20→    ///     In addition to command-side operations, the service publishes domain
    21→    ///     events through an <see cref="IEventBus"/>, allowing downstream modules
    22→    ///     (wallet UI, indexer, governance, etc.) to react in an event-driven way.
    23→    /// </summary>
