## 7. Migration Plan

### 7.1 Phased Rollout

| Phase | Description | Duration | Rollback Plan |
|-------|-------------|----------|---------------|
| **Phase 1** | Deploy RabbitMQ cluster; add configuration | 1 week | Remove config |
| **Phase 2** | Implement dual-write (in-memory + outbox) | 2 weeks | Disable outbox |
| **Phase 3** | Deploy outbox relay service | 1 week | Stop relay service |
| **Phase 4** | Migrate non-critical events (telemetry, logging) | 2 weeks | Feature flag |
| **Phase 5** | Migrate critical events (consensus, transactions) | 3 weeks | Feature flag |
| **Phase 6** | Remove in-memory bus; full external | 1 week | Re-enable in-memory |

